---
title: Bacon & Veggie Fried Rice with Oyster Sauce Greens & Crispy Shallots
description: Is there anything better than fried rice? How about fried rice with everyones favourite - bacon! Elevate your fried rice experience
with savory bacon, fresh veggies, and a dusting of crispy shallots. This much-loved dish just had a make-over!
